        </p>

        <p>
        The continuous support we gain from friends, patrons, sponsors, and volunteers enables us to foster educational growth amongst aspiring young musicians with our annual music events. The enthusiasm and generosity of our patrons also help fund our Scholarship Endowment Program, which provides deserving and talented musicians scholarships towards their further pursuit in music. It is with these kind sponsorships that the United States Open Music Competition can be maintained as a world-class event.
